<dl class="method">
<dt id="DBUtil.DeploymentUnit.DeploymentUnit.add_du_logo">
<code class="descname">add_du_logo</code><span class="sig-paren">(</span><em>short_path</em>, <em>thumbnail_path</em>, <em>object_id</em><span class="sig-paren">)</span><a class="headerlink" href="#DBUtil.DeploymentUnit.DeploymentUnit.add_du_logo" title="Permalink to this definition">¶</a></dt>
<dd><p>General description:</p>
<dl class="docutils">
<dt>Args:</dt>
<dd><p class="first">param 1 : object_id(object) : This is the unique id of the            Tool stored in the database.</p>
<p>param 2 : short_path(string) : This is the parameter which has details             for path where the logo file is present for a tool .</p>
<p class="last">param 3 : thumbnail_path(string) : This is the parameter which has details             for path where the thumbnail logo file is present for a tool</p>
</dd>
<dt>Returns:</dt>
